Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.68,0:00:09.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,The countless flowers,\Nenveloped in light...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.73,0:00:20.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,...gaze at tomorrow\Nwith unwavering eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.34,0:00:39.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,Everyone wishes for me to be pure...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.35,0:00:46.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,...but what can I bring\Nwith me to the frayed skies?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.81,0:00:53.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,What I've made my own\Nby breaking off flowers in bloom...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.90,0:00:59.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,All such sinful things...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.58,0:01:07.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why did I stop making\Npromises with the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.01,0:01:14.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because even if I try\Nto run far from all the pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.28,0:01:20.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,...a cold wind rustles\Nmy hair... Don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.98,0:01:28.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Where can I ever find the answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.94,0:01:34.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,You said it once yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.33,0:01:36.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,That I should dismantle a Simoun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.57,0:01:40.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's there is nothing but a helix.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.83,0:01:44.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,The only thing we're\Ncapable of understanding is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.04,0:01:48.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,You can see something!\NWhat... What can you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.04,0:01:58.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,One, and Then Another
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.87,0:02:24.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.35,0:02:27.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm going to use\Nthese to build a cradle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.37,0:02:29.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,A cradle?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.10,0:02:33.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Where I grew up, we used to set\Nout cradles like this every spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.77,0:02:38.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,For those who passed too soon\Nto at least know a peaceful sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.85,0:02:48.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,That one's too thick.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.39,0:02:51.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,How's Dominüra?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.19,0:02:58.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't know what made\NDominüra break down, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.41,0:03:00.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,...Rimone,\Nyou should stay by her side.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.82,0:03:02.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.32,0:03:06.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,Of us all, you're the one\Nclosest to Dominüra.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:17.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.60,0:03:32.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril... So nothing happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.23,0:03:35.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's right. Nothing happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.75,0:03:40.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,The enemy's aerial base has\Nvanished. Though I don't know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.36,0:03:42.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,And nothing else happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.40,0:03:43.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.53,0:03:46.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.54,0:03:51.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.89,0:04:15.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want you to tell me.\NWhat did Dominüra see?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.61,0:04:22.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,I never should have touched\Nsomething so sacred after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.74,0:04:27.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,I never should have touched it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.29,0:04:42.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,As you wish,\NI'll never let you touch me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.56,0:05:00.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,So warm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.53,0:05:04.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,You should get some rest today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.36,0:05:09.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,But with Dominüra in that state...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.37,0:05:11.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.33,0:05:18.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.75,0:05:22.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,We've spotted\Nthe enemy at 11 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.03,0:05:23.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,It seems they're not attacking, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.76,0:05:25.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,How's Dominüra?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.60,0:05:28.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,She still seems quite indisposed...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.51,0:05:29.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:33.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Paraietta.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.78,0:05:46.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.61,0:05:52.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wait. Neviril is exhausted. She's in\Nno condition to go back up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.37,0:05:53.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.41,0:05:58.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dominüra is currently unable to pray,\Nso for now you'll obey my orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.05,0:06:00.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,Orders, she said?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.83,0:06:02.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,It sounds like the army.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.13,0:06:10.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.48,0:06:21.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's a scouting mission.\NThere's no need for Neviril to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.24,0:06:22.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,— Kaim?\N— Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.00,0:06:46.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,To think Aer would\Njust back down like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.64,0:06:49.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,It was surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.10,0:06:52.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Before, she'd take her up even\Nif she had to drag her by the arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.51,0:06:54.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't want to see Aer acting like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.60,0:07:01.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,The best thing about Aer is\Nshe's almost aggressively positive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.60,0:07:04.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,To see her being tactful...\NIt's not like her at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.69,0:07:08.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you jealous?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.55,0:07:12.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,N-No! That's not how I feel about Aer!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.72,0:07:15.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, Rimone... Where's Aer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.12,0:07:18.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,I just saw her leaving the ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.79,0:07:21.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Leaving, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.04,0:07:22.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,I wonder why she did?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.75,0:07:24.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.92,0:07:33.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's not what you think. I was just\Nthinking of showering or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.89,0:07:36.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nobody's asking, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.06,0:07:43.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Really now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.13,0:08:09.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.96,0:08:11.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,What are you apologizing for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.26,0:08:17.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,You can't even think of a reason to,\Nbut you're just doing it anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.78,0:08:19.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,I do have a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.02,0:08:24.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,The reason you're in so much\Npain, Neviril... I know it's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.77,0:08:32.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't know why that is, but it's my\Nfault... That much I know at least, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.42,0:08:33.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't flatter yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.38,0:08:54.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Floe...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.47,0:08:56.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,That was so uncool.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.89,0:09:02.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please forgive me, Sibylla Aurea,\Nfor speaking to you so rudely.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.49,0:09:15.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,They're so alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.11,0:09:20.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Amuria... was just like that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.28,0:09:22.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,She was never really looking at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.20,0:09:28.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's right...\NI finally realized it because of Aer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.21,0:09:31.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,In their eyes, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.39,0:09:43.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,...no more than a tool to help\Nthem reach greater heights.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.60,0:09:45.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.02,0:09:54.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,I think I might have made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.74,0:10:00.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,With you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.78,0:10:02.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.28,0:10:05.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm not the person you think I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.12,0:10:10.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,If I'm not mistaken about\Nwhat you're about to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.46,0:10:17.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm sure...\Nthat it would make me waver.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.68,0:10:26.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're exhausted right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.82,0:10:29.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're not yourself. So please...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.27,0:10:30.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.94,0:10:34.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,What have I done?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.78,0:10:37.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Paraietta...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.28,0:10:39.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.45,0:10:40.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.00,0:10:52.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,Again...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.29,0:10:54.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'll go too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.43,0:10:56.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,—No. You should...\N— But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.30,0:10:58.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.51,0:11:05.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'll go for heaven's sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.56,0:11:08.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,The air's not good here anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.02,0:11:09.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,The air?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.85,0:11:12.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right, Alty?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.29,0:11:15.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,I guess, if that's what Floe wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.27,0:11:18.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,And the other will be flown\Nby Mamina and Roatreamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.78,0:11:20.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.59,0:11:38.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't know about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.01,0:11:40.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.09,0:11:43.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yun and Kaim haven't\Neven come back yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.49,0:11:46.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,And if there's no attack,\Nfor us to mobilize...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.27,0:11:47.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you implying I've\Nmade the wrong decision?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.68,0:11:51.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,I never said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.90,0:12:02.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't always be by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.70,0:12:05.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,Even so, I can at least protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.91,0:12:08.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.08,0:12:50.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's so quiet...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.25,0:12:55.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're not going to hang\Naround the Simouns today?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.37,0:12:58.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.51,0:13:03.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wanna play hide-and-seek?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.97,0:13:05.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,Treated like a child...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.58,0:13:07.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, Aer?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.02,0:13:08.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sure! Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.60,0:13:16.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right, Morinas, count to 100.\NNo cheating, got that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.25,0:13:17.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.79,0:13:18.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Here goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.98,0:13:23.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,One, two, three, four...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.86,0:13:23.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rimone! Go hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.30,0:13:31.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,...five, six, seven, eight,\Nnine, ten, eleven, twelve...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.91,0:13:33.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.14,0:13:57.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,...as blue as a tear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.19,0:14:04.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,As white as a lily...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.90,0:14:13.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,In the pitch-black darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.20,0:14:20.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,...the light of a red flame...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.17,0:14:22.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,That song...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.71,0:14:26.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's from Aer's music box...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.26,0:14:29.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,The doorway to a new frontier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.09,0:14:33.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,For those who seek a land\Nof peace... The immigrants' song.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.90,0:14:46.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Tempus Spatium embraced us, those\Nwhom had no place to call home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.11,0:14:52.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Chor Dextra was created\Nto perform the Emerald Ri Majon...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.95,0:14:57.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Its soldiers were recruited for their\Nwillingness to lay down their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.67,0:15:00.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,But none of that mattered to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.23,0:15:04.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,In return for my death,\NKyuukoku actually needed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.05,0:15:07.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,And I wanted to feel needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.68,0:15:10.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,That was what I'd always... always...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.47,0:15:12.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.22,0:15:17.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're still needed. Because I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.04,0:15:21.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to do the Emerald Ri Majon.\NI want to do it with you, Dominüra.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.19,0:15:24.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.27,0:15:28.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because you're my pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.50,0:15:48.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Paraietta, the rain\Nis coming down harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.76,0:15:51.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,This can't be good for\Nyour health. Please go inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.80,0:16:33.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.97,0:16:39.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,Do you need to see Dominüra?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.31,0:16:42.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.65,0:16:56.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why am I so indecisive? I've got\Nto do something, or I'll lose Neviril...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.05,0:17:20.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Another attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.40,0:17:34.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,It doesn't make sense, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.36,0:17:37.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't we wait for Dominüra\Nto get back to normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.75,0:17:40.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,Can't you do anything without\NDominüra instructing you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.41,0:17:43.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is no time for petty nitpicking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.41,0:17:45.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,Petty, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.84,0:17:48.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,Seriously, at this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.12,0:17:49.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.21,0:17:55.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Pair up with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.01,0:17:59.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,You and I will patrol. From now on...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.41,0:18:00.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.55,0:18:01.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.93,0:18:05.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.06,0:18:07.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Morinas, come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.02,0:18:09.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.28,0:18:11.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril, you can't go. You're still...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.71,0:18:12.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.95,0:18:15.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let me go, Paraietta.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.65,0:18:51.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.02,0:18:54.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,...powerless.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.47,0:19:31.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,What about our game\Nof hide-and-seek?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.94,0:19:40.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,She's going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.03,0:19:43.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dominüra...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.37,0:19:50.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,People who are about to die\Nhave that look in their eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.83,0:19:53.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rimone...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.69,0:20:14.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dominüra.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.78,0:20:26.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dominüra, I want you\Nto tell me what you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.00,0:20:28.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's your read on this situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.46,0:20:35.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dominüra!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.71,0:20:40.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.88,0:20:44.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Could the judgment of\Nsomeone who's been asleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.01,0:20:47.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,...be less questionable\Nthan your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.70,0:21:04.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dominüra.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.49,0:21:06.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Another helping please.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.50,0:21:22.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Emerald Ri Majon...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.46,0:21:26.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,By dismantling a Simoun...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.38,0:21:30.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,...I think that I've seen what\Nlies beyond its completion.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.02,0:21:36.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,You only think you did, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.42,0:21:39.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,You can't be sure\Nunless you really do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.57,0:21:45.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,There's no other way, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.07,0:21:51.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,The only thing you've ever\Nbeen asked to do was to fly high...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.83,0:21:55.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,To inscribe Ri Majons across\Nthe vast sky. That's precisely why...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.75,0:22:01.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,To be denied this would be the same\Nas having your own existence denied.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.59,0:22:08.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,You and I are very much alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.09,0:22:10.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,I chose you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.39,0:22:12.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,And you chose me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.77,0:22:16.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,If it's that link between us that\Nmakes a Ri Majon what it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.90,0:22:21.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm going to do it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.91,0:22:31.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Emerald Ri Majon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.25,0:22:47.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,It is played by my wounds...\Nthe song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.92,0:22:52.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let it ring out over\Nthe grieving universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.20,0:22:59.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Can we change tomorrow?\NDon't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.19,0:23:06.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to let you know\Nhow my heart's overflowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.66,0:23:19.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,"I want to get closer to you."\N"I want to feel your pulse."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.75,0:23:24.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was too defiant,\Nand I took the long way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.93,0:23:28.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,The blue moon is swaying silently.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.95,0:23:32.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,My true heart's desire is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.76,0:23:38.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't reach you.\NMy tears of pain trickle down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.85,0:23:44.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Soar away into the sky, song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.36,0:23:47.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Carrying my love that came too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.76,0:23:53.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,What can I do to change tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.41,0:23:59.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just hold on to "now" the way it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.00,0:24:06.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,To Be Continued
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.67,0:24:08.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Messis has finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.34,0:24:12.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,...become the target of\NShoukoku's mid-sized air fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.05,0:24:16.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Next time on Simoun...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.60,0:24:18.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Emerald Ri Majon.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.51,0:24:20.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Emerald Ri Majon
